## Quick Reference: Key Token Values

```css
/* Colors */
--accent: #2dd4bf (teal brand color)
--text-primary: #e8e8e8
--text-secondary: #888
--surface: #131313

/* Typography */
Hero H1: clamp(34px, 4.5vw, 52px), weight 700
Body: 16px, weight 400, line-height 1.8

/* Spacing */
--nav-h: 64px
--max-w: 1120px
--side-pad: clamp(24px, 5vw, 64px)
Section bottom margin: 80px or 120px

/* Motion */
--transition: 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1)
--transition-fast: 0.15s ease

/* Layout */
Pillars: 2-column grid (768px breaks to 1)
Cases: Single-column stack with 200px image column
Responsive breakpoints: 768px (tablet), 480px (mobile)
```

---

## When in Doubt
1. Check `DESIGN.md` for token values and patterns
2. Look at existing similar components in `styles.css`
3. Test in Cursor's Visual Editor before finalizing
4. Verify mobile responsiveness (use Chrome DevTools)
5. Run through accessibility checklist (contrast, focus, keyboard nav)

